title: Two men cleared of Scarlett Keeling murder back in court
text: Two men acquitted of raping and murdering British teenager Scarlett Keeling in Goa in 2008 will face court again Scarlett Keeling's bruised body was found on a beach in Goa in 2008 She had drugs included cocaine in her system and there was evidence of assault Samson dâ€™Souza and Placido Carvalho were charged but cleared of the offences They will be hauled back before the courts after India's Central Bureau of Investigation announced it would appeal the acquittal
